## Deep Dive Into Modern Web Development (Full Stack Open)

**Deep Dive Into Modern Web Development (Full Stack Open)** is a comprehensive course that covers the essential concepts and technologies of modern web development. The course focuses on building full-stack applications using JavaScript, React, Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and GraphQL. It emphasizes hands-on learning through practical projects and exercises, enabling students to gain real-world experience in developing scalable and maintainable web applications. Topics include RESTful APIs, authentication, testing, deployment, and continuous integration. The course is suitable for both beginners and developers looking to deepen their understanding of current web development practices.
